{"image_id": "UNM_2014_page_117", "image_size": [1238, 1632], "ocr": [{"text": "Unum • 2014 Annual Report", "bbox": [861.7, 1540.6, 1103.9, 1596.5]}, {"text": "115", "bbox": [1138.0, 1557.8, 1163.0, 1576.6]}, {"text": "We evaluate each of our mortgage loans individually for impairment and assign an internal credit quality rating based on a", "bbox": [150.1, 233.3, 1087.3, 254.3]}, {"text": "comprehensive rating system used to evaluate the credit risk of the loan. The factors we use to derive our internal credit ratings may", "bbox": [112.5, 262.5, 1125.9, 283.5]}, {"text": "include the following:", "bbox": [112.5, 291.7, 277.2, 312.7]}, {"text": "• \u0007Loan-to-value ratio", "bbox": [150.1, 320.9, 302.3, 341.9]}, {"text": "• \u0007Debt service coverage ratio based on current operating income", "bbox": [150.1, 350.1, 633.5, 371.1]}, {"text": "• \u0007Property location, including regional economics, trends and demographics", "bbox": [150.1, 379.3, 718.1, 400.3]}, {"text": "• \u0007Age, condition, and construction quality of property", "bbox": [150.1, 408.5, 546.7, 429.5]}, {"text": "• \u0007Current and historical occupancy of property", "bbox": [150.1, 437.7, 491.4, 458.7]}, {"text": "• \u0007Lease terms relative to market", "bbox": [150.1, 466.9, 387.9, 487.8]}, {"text": "• \u0007Tenant size and financial strength", "bbox": [150.1, 496.0, 410.0, 517.0]}, {"text": "• \u0007Borrower’s financial strength", "bbox": [150.1, 525.2, 375.6, 546.2]}, {"text": "• \u0007Borrower’s equity in transaction", "bbox": [150.1, 554.4, 400.5, 575.4]}, {"text": "• \u0007Additional collateral, if any", "bbox": [150.1, 583.6, 358.9, 604.6]}, {"text": "Although all available and applicable factors are considered in our analysis, loan-to-value and debt service coverage ratios are", "bbox": [150.1, 627.4, 1114.7, 648.4]}, {"text": "the most critical factors in determining whether we will initially issue the loan and also in assigning values and determining impairment.", "bbox": [112.5, 656.6, 1159.3, 677.5]}, {"text": "We assign an overall rating to each loan using an internal rating scale of Aa (highest quality) to B (lowest quality). We review and adjust,", "bbox": [112.5, 685.7, 1147.2, 706.7]}, {"text": "as needed, our internal credit quality ratings on an annual basis. This review process is performed more frequently for mortgage loans", "bbox": [112.5, 714.9, 1125.3, 735.9]}, {"text": "deemed to have a higher risk of delinquency.", "bbox": [112.5, 744.1, 452.2, 765.1]}, {"text": "Mortgage loans, sorted by the applicable credit quality indicators, are as follows:", "bbox": [150.1, 773.3, 753.8, 794.3]}, {"text": "December 31", "bbox": [911.5, 814.6, 1001.8, 833.3]}, {"text": "(in millions of dollars)", "bbox": [112.5, 842.8, 264.2, 861.4]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [865.1, 842.7, 905.0, 861.5]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1041.4, 842.8, 1075.4, 861.4]}, {"text": "Internal Rating", "bbox": [112.5, 873.0, 233.0, 894.3]}, {"text": "Aa", "bbox": [137.5, 902.4, 167.8, 923.4]}, {"text": "$       7.7", "bbox": [831.6, 902.3, 905.6, 923.4]}, {"text": "$     10.8", "bbox": [1009.3, 902.4, 1075.4, 923.4]}, {"text": "A", "bbox": [137.5, 931.6, 167.8, 952.6]}, {"text": "666.0", "bbox": [856.1, 931.5, 905.6, 952.6]}, {"text": "683.1", "bbox": [1032.8, 931.6, 1075.4, 952.6]}, {"text": "Baa", "bbox": [137.5, 960.8, 171.1, 981.8]}, {"text": "1,156.7", "bbox": [841.5, 960.7, 905.6, 981.8]}, {"text": "1,094.6", "bbox": [1018.8, 960.8, 1075.4, 981.8]}, {"text": "Ba", "bbox": [137.5, 990.0, 167.8, 1011.0]}, {"text": "13.1", "bbox": [866.0, 989.9, 905.6, 1011.0]}, {"text": "13.5", "bbox": [1042.3, 990.0, 1075.4, 1011.0]}, {"text": "B", "bbox": [137.5, 1019.2, 167.8, 1040.2]}, {"text": "13.1", "bbox": [866.0, 1019.1, 905.6, 1040.2]}, {"text": "13.1", "bbox": [1042.3, 1019.2, 1075.4, 1040.2]}, {"text": "Total", "bbox": [112.5, 1048.1, 167.8, 1069.4]}, {"text": "$1,856.6", "bbox": [831.6, 1048.2, 905.6, 1069.4]}, {"text": "$1,815.1", "bbox": [1009.3, 1048.4, 1075.4, 1069.